Setting up the application to run the first time
================================================
Setup the database
cp config/examples/database.yml config

Setup the configuration files
cp config/examples/config.yml config

Setup the deployment files
cp config/examples/deploy.rb config
mkdir config/deploy
cp config/examples/deploy/*.rb config/deploy

Set up the hosts (e.g. for "galaunia.co.dev" we're using a 3 levels for the TLD)
Add:
127.0.0.1	sangwapo.dev		www.sangwapo.dev

Set up symbolic links to the externalised assets:
cd [APP_FOLDER]/app/assets/images/housing_projects
ln -s ~/Dropbox/Galaunia\ Farms/Website/Images/Roan\ Park\ Phase\ 1/ roanparkphase1_images

cd [APP_FOLDER]/app/assets/images
ln -s ~/Dropbox/Galaunia\ Farms/Website/Images/Newsletters/ newsletters_images

cd [APP_FOLDER]/app/assets/pdfs/housing_projects
ln -s ~/Dropbox/Galaunia\ Farms/Website/PDFs/Roan\ Park\ Phase\ 1/ roanparkphase1_pdfs

cd [APP_FOLDER]/app/assets/pdfs
ln -s ~/Dropbox/Galaunia\ Farms/Website/PDFs/Newsletters/ newsletters_pdfs

Setup deployment references:
git remote add production galaunia.co.zm:/var/Repositories/Git/Galaunia.git




Testing
=======

# Guard for testing
gem cleanup
bundle update
rake db:drop
rake db:setup
rake db:test:prepare
bundle exec guard




Gem management
==============

MAINTAIN GEM BUNDLE
bundle update
gem cleanup

DELETE ALL INSTALLED GEMS
gem list | cut -d" " -f1 | xargs gem uninstall -aIx




Application Deployment
======================

# Capistrano for non-initial deployment
# STAGING DEPLOYMENT
git checkout master
git merge work
git push
git push production
cap deploy

# Capistrano for non-initial deployment
# PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT
git checkout master
git merge work
git push
git push production
cap production deploy
git tag "`date +published_%Y-%m-%d_%H%M%S`"
